  "name": "Warden's Black Autumn Cloak +3",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This cloak is a deep black, with subtle hints of amber and crimson, resembling the colors of autumn leaves at dusk.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Shadow's Embrace:</strong> Grants a +10 on escape artist checks. Nothing sticks to the fabric and it slips and flows through any grip like water.</li><li><strong>Harvest's Fortune:</strong> Once per day, the wearer can cast <em>Entangle</em> as a spell-like ability.</li></ul><p>History: Worn by Thorn Blackthorn, the group's rogue, this cloak helped him escape danger and manipulate the environment to his advantage.</p><p></p><p>Constant @UUID[Compendium.pf1.spells.Item.pau0ejk30fs1eebl]{Endure Elements} effect.</p><img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/cloaks/cloak_childs_brick_red_fleece_traveling_cloak_with_simple_.webp\" />",
